Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平胡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:05.89,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HB1FCF9&}{\1c&HBB6066&}啊啊 喜歡是動搖人心之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是天界服務技術第一的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也敵不過她的好運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我把機車推出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多好去完成另一項任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的另一項任務…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也鬧得夠嗆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近天天都那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些話要對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 你對蓓兒丹蒂好好地說過喜歡她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼要說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這次任務中 一直觀察著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你實在太缺乏積極性了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能就這樣放著你們不管 背負敗名回到天界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈什麼哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我該…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 你對女性要更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思 馬上就去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為你能逃得掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要讓你說出「喜歡」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這裏是WHIRLWIND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 今天照常營業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉原的消聲器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可以免費送貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「說過喜歡她嗎」…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是喜歡 可是真要說出口…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會傳染吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來喝下午茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子果然是被說「喜歡」會比較開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要對我告白我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:06:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原來如此 森裏難道認為即使不說出來對方也能理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.32,0:06:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子啊 一直都很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在追尋著確認的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"喜歡"這句話 比起上百個禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能讓女孩子感動和安心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的話 就趕緊行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏他有件很重要的事要對蓓兒說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡森裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 森裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下人才交流中心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是禮拜天 應該不開門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒種的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來再好好教訓你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是沒種呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來要下猛藥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎 要說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喜歡」嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有多少年沒聽到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喜歡」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨處可見的簡單詞彙 卻包含著重要含義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,街上洋溢著「喜歡」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對她 對最愛的她傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好猶豫的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得 現在應該能說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\ann8}（最喜歡貓實市了！）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是沒說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別做了 不適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 歡迎回來 螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭 怕什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不會把你吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特·訓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 把我當成蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 對我說「喜歡」 來練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種話 就這麼隨隨便便說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會這麼想 是因為心裏有一個限製器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你知道「喜歡」這個詞包含著無窮的含義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要把這個限製器給破壞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的那份心意 就能夠隨時加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（限製器嗎…真會說話）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 打開心靈的加速器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語言如旋律 思念如歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更用心一些 搖動對方的心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的旋律能抵達 我的心也會動搖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 不過還是不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再強烈一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（對 我想要自己親口傳達）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（蓓兒丹蒂…想對你傳達）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動搖了 但是還要更…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對她傳達的話 這種程度還遠遠不夠！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一　洗澡水放好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵　這下有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是… 等等！這是誤會！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你遇到麻煩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有很深的煩惱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德 你又偷聽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是愛之丘比特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要告訴我 隨時都能為你排憂解難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想說「喜歡」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Je t'aime（法語）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你（漢語）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ich liebe dich（德語）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chan rak khun（泰語）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ti amo（意大利語）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Te amo（西班牙語）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,****
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(韓語)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Я любю тебя（俄語）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪兒學來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單單這樣練習是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是發自內心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 對臉皮薄的螢一來說很難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很開心啊 兀兒德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 我是在擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我特別為你準備了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是吃了這東西 不知道會變成什麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這樣說我的藥也太失禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你自己吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 讓我們看看這藥的效果是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀…兀兒德？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩歐絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩歐絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的……還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這藥的效果不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 兀兒德老是搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩歐絲你不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說了 看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 為什麼那麼在意我的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是因為我是女神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你幸福是我的使命 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是因為螢一的周圍散發著一種「無法放任不管光環」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「無法放任不管光環」？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 又開始散發了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…讓人放心不下的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這麼亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:17:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼啊 你的陰謀已經被我看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才被你擺了一道 到底那是什麼藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼危險的東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喜歡」不是光用語言就能傳達的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是對於像螢一這樣的男孩子來說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我製作了這個僅僅增幅"喜歡"\N這個詞的力量的特殊增幅藥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 聽上去很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…剛才…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我只是稍微有點吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是某種練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:18:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…稍微有點羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羨慕？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 無論何時聽到「喜歡」這個詞 總是會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是螢一所說的話…那就更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（女孩子啊 一直都很不安）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了要對你說喜歡而…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（喜歡喜歡喜歡…）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？說了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂！你怎麼了？蓓兒丹蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太…太…太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太穢褻了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想對我的姐姐做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不給出合理解釋不會放過你哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誤會 我什麼都沒做！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是為了說出「喜歡」…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（喜歡喜歡喜歡…）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 為什麼效力那麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為接受了我的特訓嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德 佩歐絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是你們搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我可什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才不是還說了「多虧了我的特訓」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 還不是因為你那奇怪的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我的藥奇怪是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是實話實說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩歐絲的特訓才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打架我奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去可怎麼辦 想殺了我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：想杀了我吗？（ころすきか？）包含了关键词すき
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（喜歡！喜歡！喜歡！…）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…不好意思…有誰來幫我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32\pos(685,55)}{\clip(685,23,718,55)\t(\clip(685,55,718,279))}果\N然\N是\N危\N險\N的\N藥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32\pos(685,55)}果\N然\N是\N危\N險\N的\N藥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 把我當實驗品有啥開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 剛才我都六神無主了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺…成百上千的螢一的感情涌入心中…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然嚇了一跳 但是非常幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喜歡」這個詞 真是太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（佩歐絲就是為了這個…）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 剛才沒有好好地向你傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…剛才暈了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請你再說一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.26,0:21:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我會好好聽著的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是最喜歡的人所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好謝謝佩歐絲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她提供了這個契機 讓我有了向你傳達這份心意的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：说出来的契机（出すきっかけ）包含了すき…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣叫我怎麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次…下次一定會好好聽著的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.77,0:22:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是讓人放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 真是太沒出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓你對姐姐說「喜歡」呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森裏有沒有說出來啊
